statements: SELECT * FROM tax_brackets;
SELECT id, income_range, tax_rate FROM tax_brackets;
SELECT * FROM tax_brackets WHERE income_range >= 50000;
SELECT id, tax_rate FROM tax_brackets WHERE income_range < 30000;
SELECT id, income_range, tax_rate FROM tax_brackets WHERE tax_rate > 0.2;
SELECT * FROM tax_brackets WHERE income_range > 50000 ORDER BY tax_rate DESC;
SELECT id, tax_rate FROM tax_brackets WHERE income_range BETWEEN 20000 AND 80000;
SELECT * FROM tax_brackets WHERE tax_rate < 0.3 ORDER BY income_range ASC;
SELECT id, income_range, tax_rate FROM tax_brackets WHERE income_range < 30000 AND tax_rate > 0.25;
SELECT income_range, SUM(tax_rate) AS total_tax FROM tax_brackets GROUP BY income_range ORDER BY total_tax DESC;
SELECT * FROM clients;
SELECT client_id, client_name FROM clients WHERE income >= 50000;
SELECT client_name, income FROM clients WHERE client_id = 3;
SELECT client_name, tax_rate FROM clients JOIN tax_brackets ON clients.tax_bracket_id = tax_brackets.bracket_id;
SELECT * FROM tax_brackets WHERE tax_rate BETWEEN 20 AND 30;
SELECT * FROM clients WHERE income > 50000;
SELECT client_id, client_name, income FROM clients WHERE tax_bracket_id = 3 ORDER BY income DESC;
SELECT MAX(income_range_max) AS max_income FROM tax_brackets;
SELECT client_name, tax_rate FROM clients JOIN tax_brackets ON clients.tax_bracket_id = tax_brackets.bracket_id WHERE tax_rate > 0.25;
SELECT client_id, client_name, income, tax_rate FROM clients JOIN tax_brackets ON clients.tax_bracket_id = tax_brackets.bracket_id WHERE income_range_min < 50000 ORDER BY tax_rate ASC;
SELECT * FROM tax_brackets ORDER BY tax_rate DESC;
SELECT client_name, client_income FROM clients WHERE client_income > 50000;
SELECT client_name, tax_due FROM clients JOIN tax_calculations ON clients.client_id = tax_calculations.client_id WHERE tax_due > 1000;
SELECT * FROM tax_calculations ORDER BY taxable_income ASC;
SELECT DISTINCT min_income, max_income FROM tax_brackets ORDER BY max_income DESC;
SELECT * FROM tax_brackets ORDER BY tax_rate DESC, min_income ASC;
SELECT client_name, client_income, taxable_income FROM clients JOIN tax_calculations ON clients.client_id = tax_calculations.client_id;
SELECT client_name, tax_due FROM clients JOIN tax_calculations ON clients.client_id = tax_calculations.client_id WHERE tax_due > 1000;
SELECT * FROM tax_calculations WHERE taxable_income BETWEEN 50000 AND 80000;
SELECT client_name, tax_due FROM clients JOIN tax_calculations ON clients.client_id = tax_calculations.client_id ORDER BY client_name ASC, tax_due DESC;
SELECT * FROM tax_brackets;
SELECT max_income, tax_rate FROM tax_brackets WHERE min_income < 50000;
SELECT name, email FROM clients ORDER BY name ASC;
SELECT client_id, tax_owed FROM client_tax_info WHERE taxable_income > 100000 ORDER BY tax_owed DESC;
SELECT tax_year, total_tax_paid FROM tax_history WHERE client_id = 101 AND tax_year = 2021;
SELECT * FROM tax_brackets ORDER BY min_income DESC;
SELECT name, email FROM clients WHERE phone_number LIKE '%123%';
SELECT client_id, taxable_income, tax_owed FROM client_tax_info WHERE taxable_income > 50000 AND tax_owed < 1000;
SELECT tax_year, total_tax_paid FROM tax_history WHERE total_tax_paid > 5000 ORDER BY tax_year ASC;
SELECT t.tax_rate, c.name, ci.taxable_income FROM tax_brackets t JOIN clients c ON t.id = c.client_id JOIN client_tax_info ci ON c.client_id = ci.client_id;
SELECT * FROM tax_bracket;
SELECT id, bracket_name, tax_rate FROM tax_bracket WHERE tax_rate > 0.2 ORDER BY bracket_name DESC;
SELECT client_name, client_type FROM client WHERE client_type = 'Individual' LIMIT 5;
SELECT client_id, income_amount, income_date FROM income WHERE income_amount > 50000 AND income_date >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT payment_amount, payment_date FROM payment WHERE payment_amount < 1000 ORDER BY payment_date ASC;
SELECT * FROM tax_bracket ORDER BY bracket_name DESC, tax_rate ASC;
SELECT client_name, client_type FROM client WHERE tax_bracket_id = 1;
SELECT income_amount, income_date FROM income WHERE income_amount > 10000 ORDER BY income_date DESC;
SELECT payment_amount, client_id FROM payment WHERE payment_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31';

SELECT client.client_name, tax_calculation.total_tax_paid FROM client JOIN tax_calculation ON client.id = tax_calculation.client_id WHERE tax_calculation.total_tax_paid > 5000 ORDER BY client.client_name ASC;
